        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "model",
              "value": "MiniMax-M3"
            },
            {
              "name": "messages",
              "value": "={{ \n[\n  {\n    \"role\": \"user\",\n    \"content\": `You are an expert AI immigration news analyst. Analyze the following news item and output JSON strictly conforming to the requested format.\n\nNews Title: ${$json.title}\nNews Content: ${$json.contentSnippet}\n\nPlease translate the title and summary to EN and ZH, provide tags (country_tags, topic_tags, audience_tags), multi-dimensional scores (0-100: importance_score, video_score, chinese_relevance_score, evergreen_score), extract keywords, write an ai_analysis, generate youtube_suggestions, and determine official_source.\n\nYou must return ONLY valid JSON conforming exactly to this structure (flat keys for translations):\n{\n  \"title_en\": \"English title translation\",\n  \"title_zh\": \"Chinese title translation\",\n  \"summary_en\": \"English summary translation\",\n  \"summary_zh\": \"Chinese summary translation\",\n  \"country_tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"],\n  \"topic_tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"],\n  \"audience_tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"],\n  \"importance_score\": 50,\n  \"video_score\": 50,\n  \"chinese_relevance_score\": 50,\n  \"evergreen_score\": 50,\n  \"keywords\": [\"keyword1\"],\n  \"ai_analysis\": \"AI analysis text\",\n  \"youtube_suggestions\": {\n    \"titles\": [\"YouTube title option 1\", \"YouTube title option 2\"],\n    \"thumbnail_prompt\": \"Description of a matching thumbnail image\"\n  },\n  \"official_source\": false\n}`\n  }\n]\n}}"
            },
            {
              "name": "max_tokens",
              "value": "={{ 4000 }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
